00:34:57.050 --> 00:34:59.250
sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:34:59.250 --> 00:35:04.550
يَا أَيُّهَا الْمُدَّثِّرْ

00:35:04.550 --> 00:35:07.450
قُمْ فَأَنذِرْ

00:35:07.450 --> 00:35:10.250
وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرْ

00:35:10.250 --> 00:35:13.150
وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرْ

00:35:13.150 --> 00:35:15.550
وَالْرُّجْزَ فَهْجُرْ

00:35:15.550 --> 00:35:20.350
وَلَا تَمْنُونْ تَسْتَكْثِرْ

00:35:20.350 --> 00:35:22.750
وَلِ رَبِّكَ فَصْبِرْ

00:35:22.750 --> 00:35:24.150
those are the verses

00:35:24.150 --> 00:35:25.550
they came down

00:35:25.550 --> 00:35:27.350
that was now an instruction

00:35:27.350 --> 00:35:29.150
let's go through the meaning of it

00:35:29.150 --> 00:35:30.650
يَا أَيُّهَا الْمُدَّثِّرْ

00:35:30.650 --> 00:35:34.950
oh you who is enveloped in garments

00:35:34.950 --> 00:35:36.550
he was already enveloped in garments

00:35:36.550 --> 00:35:39.250
covered in garments

00:35:39.250 --> 00:35:40.350
قُمْ فَأَنذِرْ

00:35:40.350 --> 00:35:41.750
get up and warn

00:35:41.750 --> 00:35:42.950
so he was now instructed

00:35:42.950 --> 00:35:44.250
to deliver the message

00:35:44.250 --> 00:35:44.950
get up

00:35:44.950 --> 00:35:46.450
and you know to get up means

00:35:46.450 --> 00:35:47.050
be brave

00:35:47.050 --> 00:35:47.650
get up

00:35:47.650 --> 00:35:48.350
don't worry

00:35:48.350 --> 00:35:49.350
Allah is there

00:35:49.350 --> 00:35:50.050
if someone tells you

00:35:50.050 --> 00:35:51.450
get up and walk

00:35:51.450 --> 00:35:53.250
or get up and tell the people

