it's much more stronger

00:35:56.250 --> 00:35:57.750
than a person who tells you

00:35:57.750 --> 00:35:58.750
just sit down and quietly

00:35:58.750 --> 00:36:00.750
just mention this

00:36:00.750 --> 00:36:01.450
stand up

00:36:01.450 --> 00:36:02.550
eloquence

00:36:02.550 --> 00:36:03.250
it is a message

00:36:03.250 --> 00:36:04.250
a powerful message

00:36:04.250 --> 00:36:05.150
get up and warn

00:36:05.150 --> 00:36:06.750
from this we know the sunnah

00:36:06.750 --> 00:36:08.950
when Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:36:08.950 --> 00:36:10.650
used to deliver his sermons

00:36:10.650 --> 00:36:12.050
ninety percent of the time

00:36:12.050 --> 00:36:12.850
if not more

00:36:12.850 --> 00:36:14.850
he was standing

00:36:14.850 --> 00:36:15.750
unless there was a reason

00:36:15.750 --> 00:36:17.350
for him to sit

00:36:17.350 --> 00:36:18.450
he was standing

00:36:18.450 --> 00:36:19.250
so this is the sunnah

00:36:19.250 --> 00:36:20.150
قُمْ فَأَنذِرْ

00:36:20.150 --> 00:36:21.250
get up and warn

00:36:21.250 --> 00:36:23.050
warn who

00:36:23.050 --> 00:36:23.850
the people

00:36:23.850 --> 00:36:24.750
warn those

00:36:24.750 --> 00:36:26.250
and Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:36:26.250 --> 00:36:27.650
then later on

00:36:27.650 --> 00:36:28.950
broadened the circle

00:36:28.950 --> 00:36:30.750
