00:36:30.750 --> 00:36:31.450
قُمْ فَأَنذِرْ

00:36:31.450 --> 00:36:33.150
وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرْ

00:36:33.150 --> 00:36:34.850
and your Rabb

00:36:34.850 --> 00:36:36.150
He is the one

00:36:36.150 --> 00:36:37.550
whom you should declare

00:36:37.550 --> 00:36:38.550
the greatness of

00:36:38.550 --> 00:36:39.650
nobody else

00:36:39.650 --> 00:36:41.350
so we neither worship sticks

00:36:41.350 --> 00:36:41.950
no stones

00:36:41.950 --> 00:36:42.550
no idols

00:36:42.550 --> 00:36:43.050
nothing

00:36:43.050 --> 00:36:43.850
no takbeer

00:36:43.850 --> 00:36:45.550
