00:36:45.550 --> 00:36:46.250
nothing

00:36:46.250 --> 00:36:47.450
the greatest is always

00:36:47.450 --> 00:36:48.550
Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:36:48.550 --> 00:36:49.550
Allah أكبر

00:36:49.550 --> 00:36:50.850
Allah is the greatest

00:36:50.850 --> 00:36:52.550
so رَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرْ

