when we want to give a message

00:37:14.950 --> 00:37:17.050
we need to be presentable

00:37:17.050 --> 00:37:19.750
presentable according to what we have

00:37:19.750 --> 00:37:21.550
sometimes people may not have

00:37:21.550 --> 00:37:23.550
there were times when Nabi صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:37:23.550 --> 00:37:25.050
