when Allah has blessed you

00:37:43.850 --> 00:37:45.250
then the blessing of Allah

00:37:45.250 --> 00:37:46.650
should be visible on you

00:37:46.650 --> 00:37:49.550
thank Allah by using what he gave you

00:37:49.550 --> 00:37:51.050
so those who now

00:37:51.050 --> 00:37:52.250
and I have seen some brothers

00:37:52.250 --> 00:37:53.350
Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:37:53.350 --> 00:37:54.750
guide me, guide us all

00:37:54.750 --> 00:37:56.750
who intentionally make patches

00:37:56.850 --> 00:37:58.350
and instead of you know

00:37:58.350 --> 00:37:59.850
just admitting that they following

00:37:59.850 --> 00:38:00.950
styles and designs

