grant us a deep understanding

00:38:19.050 --> 00:38:20.050
so Allah is saying

00:38:20.050 --> 00:38:21.750
ثيابك فطهر

00:38:21.750 --> 00:38:23.050
والرجز فهجر

00:38:23.050 --> 00:38:25.150
everything dirty, impure

00:38:25.150 --> 00:38:25.950
leave it

