whether it is bad character

00:38:27.450 --> 00:38:29.250
bad conduct, bad behavior

00:38:29.250 --> 00:38:31.050
foul language, impurity

00:38:31.050 --> 00:38:32.150
in terms of worship

00:38:32.150 --> 00:38:34.250
all that, chase it away

00:38:34.250 --> 00:38:36.350
be far away from that

00:38:36.350 --> 00:38:38.750
ولا تمنون تستكثر

00:38:38.750 --> 00:38:41.550
and do not go and brag

00:38:41.550 --> 00:38:43.450
about something you've done

00:38:43.450 --> 00:38:44.950
in order to try and get more

00:38:44.950 --> 00:38:45.950
or raise attention

00:38:45.950 --> 00:38:47.950
today we do something small

00:38:47.950 --> 00:38:49.350
and then we want the whole world

00:38:49.350 --> 00:38:50.750
to know we did this

00:38:50.750 --> 00:38:52.350
there are very few who will tell you

00:38:52.350 --> 00:38:53.450
I don't want to be known

00:38:53.450 --> 00:38:54.450
Allahu Akbar

00:38:54.450 --> 00:38:55.850
and they will stick to that

00:38:55.850 --> 00:38:57.550
may Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:38:57.550 --> 00:38:58.450
bless us all

00:38:58.450 --> 00:39:01.150
sometimes we do a small favor for someone

00:39:01.150 --> 00:39:03.150
but the way we brag about it

00:39:03.150 --> 00:39:05.150
they actually begin to feel that

00:39:05.150 --> 00:39:06.350
I hope that this man

00:39:06.350 --> 00:39:07.950
had not done me this favor

00:39:07.950 --> 00:39:09.150
because the bragging of it

00:39:09.150 --> 00:39:10.750
is far more valuable

00:39:10.750 --> 00:39:11.850
or far more

00:39:11.850 --> 00:39:14.050
it has exceeded the value of the gift

00:39:14.050 --> 00:39:16.050
they actually have engaged in

00:39:16.050 --> 00:39:17.350
may Allah protect us

00:39:17.350 --> 00:39:18.750
this does not mean we should forget

00:39:18.750 --> 00:39:20.150
the goodness someone has done to us

00:39:20.150 --> 00:39:22.350
but it does mean when we do good

00:39:22.350 --> 00:39:23.850
we should forget it

00:39:23.850 --> 00:39:25.350
do it for the sake of Allah

00:39:25.350 --> 00:39:29.150
اِنَّمَا نُطُعِمُكُمْ لِوَجَيْهِ اللَّهِ

00:39:29.150 --> 00:39:35.950
لا نُرِيدُ مِنكُمْ جَزَاءٌ وَلَا شُكُورًا

00:39:35.950 --> 00:39:37.150
in Surah Al-Dahra

00:39:37.150 --> 00:39:38.250
Allah says

00:39:38.250 --> 00:39:40.550
indeed we feed you for the sake of Allah

00:39:40.550 --> 00:39:43.050
we don't want from you any recompense

00:39:43.050 --> 00:39:44.450
nor do we want a thanks

00:39:44.450 --> 00:39:46.450
we just will suffice with the reward

00:39:46.450 --> 00:39:47.650
that Allah has given us

00:39:47.650 --> 00:39:49.150
may Allah make us from those

00:39:49.150 --> 00:39:50.550
who can suffice with the reward

00:39:50.550 --> 00:39:51.650
that Allah has given us

00:39:51.650 --> 00:39:53.250
remember when we brag about things

00:39:53.250 --> 00:39:54.850
we reduce the reward

00:39:54.850 --> 00:39:57.150
and when we think okay it's me who did this

00:39:57.150 --> 00:39:57.950
some people come and say

00:39:57.950 --> 00:39:59.250
you know who put you on your feet

00:39:59.250 --> 00:40:00.050
it was me

00:40:00.050 --> 00:40:01.450
it wasn't you it was Allah

00:40:01.450 --> 00:40:02.850
because your feet and my feet

00:40:02.850 --> 00:40:03.850
are all in the hands of Allah

00:40:03.850 --> 00:40:05.350
subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:40:05.350 --> 00:40:06.250
we need to know that

00:40:06.250 --> 00:40:07.450
so never ever tell someone

00:40:07.450 --> 00:40:09.250
you know I'm the one who put you on the map

00:40:09.250 --> 00:40:10.250
and I'm the one who did this

00:40:10.250 --> 00:40:11.950
no, that map belongs to Allah

00:40:11.950 --> 00:40:12.750
you and me

00:40:12.750 --> 00:40:13.750
we all on that map

00:40:13.750 --> 00:40:14.750
if Allah wills

00:40:14.750 --> 00:40:16.450
and we all off it if Allah wills

00:40:16.450 --> 00:40:17.450
so it's Allah

00:40:17.450 --> 00:40:19.050
let's relate things to Allah

00:40:19.050 --> 00:40:21.950
this is why in the Quran Allah says

00:40:21.950 --> 00:40:35.950
O you who believe do not nullify the reward of your charities

00:40:35.950 --> 00:40:37.450
and your good deeds

00:40:37.450 --> 00:40:38.750
by bragging about it

00:40:38.750 --> 00:40:40.550
and by harming people after that

00:40:40.550 --> 00:40:41.250
be careful

00:40:41.250 --> 00:40:43.450
don't harm the people relax

00:40:43.450 --> 00:40:45.250
because if there is a nobleman

00:40:45.250 --> 00:40:46.250
he will come up

00:40:46.250 --> 00:40:47.850
and he will pick up the fact

00:40:47.850 --> 00:40:48.950
that you are bragging

00:40:48.950 --> 00:40:50.050
and you are harming

00:40:50.050 --> 00:40:52.450
and he will disassociate himself from you

00:40:52.450 --> 00:40:54.150
in a very beautiful way

00:40:54.150 --> 00:40:56.650
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala beautify us

00:40:56.650 --> 00:40:58.350
may He rectify our habits

00:40:58.350 --> 00:41:00.450
and may He make us from those who are humble

00:41:00.450 --> 00:41:04.050
these are the first words of instruction to Allah

00:41:04.050 --> 00:41:06.250
meaning from Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:41:06.250 --> 00:41:08.350
to Muhammad salallahu alayhi wasallam

00:41:08.350 --> 00:41:10.450
laa tam nun tas takthir

