lasted three years

00:50:43.150 --> 00:50:45.950
it was known as a da'wah al-sirriya

00:50:45.950 --> 00:50:47.050
the silent call

00:50:47.050 --> 00:50:48.750
so Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiallahu anhu

00:50:48.750 --> 00:50:51.150
went to talk to some of his friends one by one

00:50:51.150 --> 00:50:52.550
all of them accepted

00:50:52.550 --> 00:50:53.650
who were these friends

00:50:53.650 --> 00:50:55.750
and who were these people

00:50:55.750 --> 00:50:56.650
Uthman

00:50:56.650 --> 00:50:57.750
subhanallah

00:50:57.750 --> 00:50:59.850
Ibn Affan radiallahu anhu

00:50:59.850 --> 00:51:02.050
he accepted readily

00:51:02.050 --> 00:51:04.050
Abdul Rahman ibn Awf radiallahu anhu

00:51:04.050 --> 00:51:06.650
Sa'd ibn Abi Waqqas radiallahu anhu

00:51:06.650 --> 00:51:09.450
Az-Zubair ibn Al-Awwam radiallahu anhu

00:51:09.450 --> 00:51:11.950
Talhah ibn Ubaydillah radiallahu anhu

00:51:11.950 --> 00:51:13.950
these were some of the people who had accepted

00:51:13.950 --> 00:51:16.450
with the effort of Abu Bakr al-Siddiq radiallahu anhu

00:51:16.450 --> 00:51:18.450
all he had to do was go to them

00:51:18.450 --> 00:51:20.150
and tell them you know

00:51:20.150 --> 00:51:22.050
Muhammad salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:51:22.050 --> 00:51:23.350
this is what happened to him

00:51:23.350 --> 00:51:24.850
he's now a messenger of Allah

00:51:24.850 --> 00:51:26.250
and he is coming to us

00:51:26.250 --> 00:51:27.350
what is he teaching

00:51:27.350 --> 00:51:29.250
he's teaching good character, good conduct

00:51:29.250 --> 00:51:30.350
worship Allah alone

00:51:30.350 --> 00:51:32.550
no idols, no sticks, no stones

00:51:32.550 --> 00:51:33.950
respect your parents

00:51:33.950 --> 00:51:35.150
even if they are non-muslim

00:51:35.150 --> 00:51:36.550
meaning even if they are bad

00:51:36.550 --> 00:51:38.650
and they are engaging in shirk and so on

00:51:38.650 --> 00:51:39.950
you don't listen to anything

00:51:39.950 --> 00:51:41.350
wherein there is transgress

00:51:41.350 --> 00:51:42.750
of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:51:42.750 --> 00:51:44.750
but you obey the other instructions

00:51:44.750 --> 00:51:45.750
you respect them

00:51:45.750 --> 00:51:46.950
and you honor your guest

00:51:46.950 --> 00:51:48.550
you look after the rights of everyone

00:51:48.550 --> 00:51:49.450
you don't cheat people

00:51:49.450 --> 00:51:50.350
you don't steal

00:51:50.350 --> 00:51:52.350
all this was brilliant

00:51:52.350 --> 00:51:53.550
because it was

00:51:53.550 --> 00:51:55.750
elevating their status even more

00:51:55.750 --> 00:51:58.050
and they were also taught that there is a heaven

00:51:58.050 --> 00:51:59.150
there is a hell

00:51:59.150 --> 00:52:00.750
you are responsible for your deeds

00:52:00.750 --> 00:52:01.650
you are answerable

00:52:01.650 --> 00:52:03.450
you will be resurrected after you die

00:52:03.450 --> 00:52:06.250
these were the teachings of Muhammad salallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:52:06.250 --> 00:52:09.450
exactly the same teachings as Jesus may peace be upon him

00:52:09.450 --> 00:52:12.550
exactly the same teachings as Moses may peace be upon him

00:52:12.550 --> 00:52:15.150
Musa alayhi salam and Isa alayhi salam

00:52:15.150 --> 00:52:17.250
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala open our doors

00:52:17.250 --> 00:52:18.350
Insha'Allah tomorrow

00:52:18.350 --> 00:52:21.250
we will go into these early believers

00:52:21.250 --> 00:52:22.450
what happened

00:52:22.450 --> 00:52:24.950
what did they endure in the early days

00:52:24.950 --> 00:52:27.750
and then how was the announcement made to Quraysh

00:52:27.750 --> 00:52:28.950
and what happened as a result

00:52:28.950 --> 00:52:30.050
until we meet again

00:52:30.050 --> 00:52:32.750
with salallahu wa salam wa baraka ala nabina Muhammad

00:52:32.750 --> 00:52:34.050
subhanallahi bi hamdihi

00:52:34.050 --> 00:52:35.450
subhanaka allahumma bi hamdik

00:52:35.450 --> 00:52:37.150
nashhadu alla ilaha illa anta

00:52:37.150 --> 00:52:38.950
nastaghfiruka wa natubu ilayk
